parameters:
\n< Serena >It's a terrible bloodstain... Deacon said it was a
stew of blood and flesh.
\n< Serena >.......

\n< Serena >An abnormal massacre. I heard a story about it
recently. A serial murder case...?

\n< Serena >No, let's not play detective. I don't have the
ability or time for that.
\n< Serena >.......
\n< Serena >Was I attacked while sitting down...?

\n< Serena >However, these bloodstains and signs of
destruction... What kind of attack could have
caused this...?
\n< Serena >It's the door.

\n< Serena >It's locked. It's not like I have any particular
reason to be here...
\n< Serena >It's the door.
\n< Serena >It looks somewhat vacant.
\n< Serena >Terrible bloodstains... Lord Director...
終了
\n< Serena >It has completely turned into a storage room.

\n< Serena >It's not like I had any attachment to it. It's
actually a room associated with unpleasant
memories.

\n< Serena >However, I feel a little bit of loneliness in this
scene.
\n< Serena >It's the closet.
\n< Serena >Inside, there are various costumes packed tightly.
\n< Serena >Is it the shelf... I wonder.

\n< Serena >I can't tell what's inside because the previous
box is in the way. It feels like I just pushed
everything in as much as I could.
\n< Serena >It's the table.

\n< Serena >I wonder if this table will be disposed of
eventually.
